# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is inspired by **Keep a Changelog** and this project follows semantic versioning during development.

---

## [0.0.1-alpha] - 2026-03-15

Initial public foundation of the project.

### Added

- initial repository structure
- project documentation files (`README.md`, `LICENSE`, `CHANGELOG`, `VERSION`)
- Git and local environment protection files (`.gitignore`, `.env.example`)
- base folders for configuration, dashboard, modules, scripts, SQL, databases and logs
- initial development tooling configuration (`.editorconfig`, `pyproject.toml`)

### Notes

- this version represents the first public alpha state of the project
- the architecture is still under active restructuring
